{"tid":1725133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[追擊黨鐵] 和你貼BB","createTime":"2019-11-15T16:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T16:09:27.000Z","uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9f91a6812efe9b8c9e2b9da6109bf1fd3d9f9a1b","tid":1725133,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:02:37.000Z","msg":"前言：今日同朋友食飯講開黨鐵惡行，朋友同我propose咗一個方法，去令黨鐵收入減少。聽完我覺得幾得意，不過<ins>絕對唔鼓勵大家咁做</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵惡行</span></span></strong>：<br />\n- 未有發放<span style=\"color: red;\">831太子站CCTV</span><br />\n- 未有交代917東鐵線紅磡站列車出軌炒車事件<br />\n- 變本加厲配合政府宵禁，<span style=\"color: red;\">地鐵站話閂就閂</span><br />\n- 將可正常運作的閘機、售票機用布遮蓋，為求營造車站被嚴重破壞<br />\n- 多次讓<span style=\"color: red;\">警方徴用列車</span><br />\n- 聘請劣質兼職無禮粗暴對待乘客<br />\n- 只<span style=\"color: red;\">加價</span>沒有減價機制<br />\n<br />\n早前有手足以跳閘形式去表達對黨鐵不滿，但其實車資無法有效傷害黨鐵收益。除咗上蓋物業，黨鐵其中一個收入來源係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">廣告</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n究竟點樣先可以令廣告商唔再喺車站內登廣告？<br />\n噴污糟佢？打爛廣告牌？唔得。<br />\n你未開工已經被人捉到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">和平、理性、非暴力</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以有<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">&rdquo;和你貼billboard&rdquo;</span></span></strong>運動<br />\n<br />\nStep 1: 預備標語貼紙<br />\nStep 2: 撕開貼紙<br />\nStep 3: 貼上廣告billboard<br />\nStep 4: 閃人<br />\n<br />\n貼完就咁算呀？當然唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行開行埋如果大家見到 e.g. Dxxtor&rsquo;s Choice廣告上面貼住光復香港 時代革命嘅標語，大家當然要影低佢happy share！<br />\n<br />\n一班人上Facebook問下該公司係咪支持光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一班人又讚下佢哋勇敢發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬，我俾咁多錢係地鐵站度落廣告，但啲stickers阻住我嘅air time，到時黨鐵就無得唔處理，日日要搵人清，仲要加派人手守billboard。<br />\n不過一個地鐵站有咁多個廣告牌，你一邊又要捉人跳閘，我睇吓你守得幾多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*注意：<br />\n- 因為黨鐵有大量CCTV, 唔建議手足貼自己屋企附近嗰站<br />\n- 先留意附近有冇人mon住, 亦因站內可能有厚多士藍絲，所以過程一定要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>低調、快</strong></span>！絕對唔可以慢慢搽膠水或者對位。<br />\n- 最好人人都貼，好似連儂牆咁撕一貼百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0a5df920fdc63d05d47e05df96ce86f7a32aee","tid":1725133,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n比啲意見<br />\n貼紙成本貴啲 不過方便快捷"},{"pid":"959751a3efafbfbe843690c68854158317e27e25","tid":1725133,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:06:49.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"294a2b73b5a7518b9340f8b8bda2e9e0c2c3beb1","tid":1725133,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"c877fc6336289dd512586f2d503aecb37eeb10bd","tid":1725133,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:07:11.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"ff5dd987794c02963dabbb63eaf991abe0ebe311","tid":1725133,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:07:24.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"1351344441cd39f1fb7d274723a8abc93fda4a20","tid":1725133,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:07:38.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"9a22818c6b393ee3bbb5faa4f62a775d04ba2808","tid":1725133,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:08:00.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"03c8368f9fd925779394aeb7ace625167f3139bf","tid":1725133,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:08:43.000Z","msg":"推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家係咪原諒黨鐵喇？"},{"pid":"31bcee4f96dc66bd5a7274f51b43a183958ffe42","tid":1725133,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"bbede613e3cf4ba98bd48fdb86dde7b0ce602faf","tid":1725133,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:09:05.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"d6a143779547a15d09f59e3bcb4fc321ad4bb3bf","tid":1725133,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:09:17.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"bb93805fc36bbc6756147dff50efffb9a1369923","tid":1725133,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:09:27.000Z","msg":"10/10"}]}